'''菲茨罗伊峰'''（{{lang-es|Monte Fitz Roy}}；{{lang|es|Cerro Chaltén}}）位于[[南美洲|南美洲]]{{le|南巴塔哥尼亚冰原|Southern Patagonian Ice Field}}，[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]与[[智利|智利]]交界处<ref name="Acuerdo1998" /><ref name=Difrol>{{Cite web |url=http://www.difrol.cl/region-de-magallanes-y-de-la-antartica-chilena/monte-fitz-roy.html |title=Mount Fitz Roy - Difrol.cl |language=es|accessdate=2020-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180824183304/http://www.difrol.cl/region-de-magallanes-y-de-la-antartica-chilena/monte-fitz-roy.html |archive-date=2018-08-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=AndesHandBook>{{Cite web|url = http://www.andeshandbook.org/montanismo/cerro/55/Fitz_Roy|title = MONTE FITZ ROY Andes Hand Book|language = en|accessdate = 2020-08-08|archive-date = 2019-04-05|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190405231841/http://www.andeshandbook.org/montanismo/cerro/55/Fitz_Roy|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name=Lugares>{{Cite web|url = https://101lugaresincreibles.com/2012/06/la-montana-que-parece-echar-humo-fitz-roy-en-la-patagonia-argentina.html|title = La montaña que parece echar humo, en la Patagonia|website = 101 Lugares increíbles|date = 2012-06-14|language = es|accessdate = 2020-08-08|archive-date = 2020-05-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200526173542/https://101lugaresincreibles.com/2012/06/la-montana-que-parece-echar-humo-fitz-roy-en-la-patagonia-argentina.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name=InterPatagonia>{{Cite web|url = https://www.interpatagonia.com/elchalten/contemplacion-cerro-fitz-roy.html|title = La silueta del Fitz Roy|website = Inter Patagonia|language = es|accessdate = 2020-08-08|archive-date = 2019-06-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190607210636/https://www.interpatagonia.com/elchalten/contemplacion-cerro-fitz-roy.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref>，海拔3359米，相对高度1951米。菲茨罗伊峰险峻陡峭，且气候多变，常年笼罩在云雾之中，当地的{{le|特维尔切人|Tehuelche people}}称其为“Chaltén”，意思是“冒烟的山”。<ref>{{cite web | language = zh-cn | publisher = 网易旅游 | title = 绝美阿根廷 | url = http://travel.163.com/photoview/17KK0006/618.html#p=6B2I8KAO17KK0006 | date = 2010-07-08 | accessdate = 2013-04-01 | archive-date = 2013-04-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130414201055/http://travel.163.com/photoview/17KK0006/618.html#p=6B2I8KAO17KK0006 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

==名称==
Cerro是一个[[西班牙语|西班牙语]]单词，意思是山，而Chaltén是来自一个{{le|特维尔切语|Tehuelche language}}的单词，意思是“冒烟的山”，由于在山顶周围通常笼罩着的云而得名。然而，菲茨罗伊只是特维尔切语众多被称为Chaltén的山峰之一。<ref name=Moreno1879/>

==发现==
据记载，第一批看到菲茨罗伊峰的[[欧洲人|欧洲人]]是[[西班牙|西班牙]]探险家安东尼奥·德维德玛和他的同伴，他们于1783年到达了[[别德马湖|别德马湖]]畔。

[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]探险家{{le|弗朗西斯科·莫雷诺|Francisco Moreno}}于1877年3月2日看到了这座山。他把它命名为菲茨罗伊，以纪念[[罗伯特·菲茨罗伊|罗伯特·菲茨罗伊]]，他作为[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]][[小猎犬号|小猎犬号]]的船长，在1834年沿着[[圣克鲁斯河_(阿根廷)|圣克鲁斯河]]航行，绘制了[[巴塔哥尼亚|巴塔哥尼亚]]海岸的大部分地区。<ref name=Moreno1879>{{cite book|author=Francisco Moreno|title=Viaje a la Patagonia Austral|page=2|publisher=La Nacion (Elefante Blanco)|location=|year=2006|origyear=1879|language=es|isbn=987-96054-7-0|quote=Como este volcán activo no ha sido mencionado por los navegantes ni viajeros, y como el nombre de Chaltén que le dan los indios lo aplican también a otras montañas, me permito llamarle volcán Fitz Roy - English: Since this active volcano has not been mentioned by navigators or travellers, and since the name Chalten that the Indians call it is also applied to other mountains, I allow myself to name it Fitz Roy volcano}}</ref>

==现况==
[[File:Escudo_de_la_Provincia_de_Santa_Cruz.svg|200px]]
[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]和[[智利|智利]]已同意其国际边界向东绕行以越过主要峰顶<ref name=Acuerdo1998>{{cite web|author=|title=Border agreement between Chile and Argentina to determine the border from Mount Fitz Roy to Daudet|year=1998|url=http://www.difrol.cl/argentina/acuerdo-para-precisar-el-recorrido-del-limite-desde-el-monte-fitz-roy-hasta-el-cerro-daudet.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160531163246/http://www.difrol.cl/argentina/acuerdo-para-precisar-el-recorrido-del-limite-desde-el-monte-fitz-roy-hasta-el-cerro-daudet.html|language=es|date=2016-05-31|archivedate=2016-05-31|accessdate=2020-08-11}}</ref>，但到峰顶以南的{{le|穆拉隆山|Cerro Murallón}}边界的很大一部分仍然不确定<ref>{{cite web|author=|title=Map showing border between Chile and Argentina (partly undefined)|url=http://www.turismovirtual.cl/xii/xii.html|language=es|accessdate=2020-08-11|archive-date=2019-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191002234247/http://www.turismovirtual.cl/xii/xii.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。这座山是阿根廷[[圣克鲁斯省_(阿根廷)|圣克鲁斯省]]的象征，其官方图章上包括这座山峰<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://viapais.com.ar/caleta-olivia/614924-un-dia-como-hoy-se-disponia-la-adopcion-del-escudo-de-la-provincia/ |title = Un día como hoy se disponía la adopción del escudo de la provincia|website=Viapais |author = María Marta Vilchez|date = 2018-09-25 |language = es|accessdate = 2020-08-11}}</ref>。

